query:
INSERT INTO workshops (id, title, description, date, price, capacity, location) VALUES
('ws-char-design-001', 'Character Design & Illustration Workshop', 'Master the fundamentals of character creation and illustration techniques. Learn professional character design principles, anatomy, expression, and styling. Perfect for aspiring illustrators, animators, and creative professionals. Participants will develop their own original character designs and take home their portfolio-ready sketches.', DATE_ADD(NOW(), INTERVAL 14 DAY), '45', '15', 'B.Y.O. at 2-4 Edmundstone Street, West End'),
('ws-diorama-build-001', 'Diorama Building & Miniature Scene Creation', 'Create immersive miniature worlds with professional diorama-building techniques. Learn landscape design, miniature placement, lighting effects, and storytelling through scale models. This workshop covers materials selection, composition principles, and finishing techniques. Ideal for model enthusiasts, artists, and creative professionals seeking to expand their portfolio.', DATE_ADD(NOW(), INTERVAL 21 DAY), '55', '12', 'B.Y.O. at 2-4 Edmundstone Street, West End'),
('ws-tote-personalized-001', 'Personalized Tote Bag Design & Customization', 'Design and create your own professional-quality personalized tote bag using advanced textile techniques. Learn screen printing, hand-painting, embroidery basics, and vinyl application. Choose from premium canvas or organic cotton bases. Perfect for personal use, gifts, or small business ventures. All participants take home a custom, market-ready tote bag.', DATE_ADD(NOW(), INTERVAL 7 DAY), '50', '18', 'B.Y.O. at 2-4 Edmundstone Street, West End');
